 Nigerian media personality, Toke Makinwa has slammed relationship coach, Derrick Jackson for involving his wife in a video where he confessed and apologized for cheating in his marriage. Derrick Jackson had released a video where he was seated with his wife Da’Naia Jackson and admitted that he had extra-marital affairs with other women. Reacting to the video, Toke Makinwa shared a snippet of the video on her Instagram story and criticized for subjecting his wife to an uncomfortable apology that probably did not augur well with Da’Naia.